ReportText: CHEST TWO VIEWS CLINICAL INFORMATION: Cough and fever for one week. COMPARISON: None. FINDINGS: Heart, lungs and vessels normal. No pneumothorax, pleural effusion or adenopathy. No significant bone abnormality. IMPRESSION: Negative chest.
